column5: We caught these right out in front of Fishmasters Bait and Tackle shop...............Fishin is on...........Jeff
looks like the bite was on eh... glad to hear you enjoyed your day on the ice

I should have stayed were I was ...It wasgood seeing ya Jeff ..This is the big fish caught today.. Another fine day on the Grand, well for some ...My buddie Chris and I  got sunked although lost 1 at the hole ... Lots of others had great luck today ...It was a very busy day on the hard stuff with reports of a 11.5lber caught ! Looking forward to seeing the pic's on that one. ..  Not sure the name of the guy that caught this but beauty fish if your on the site say hello ..   Remeber guys if your not putting it on the wall please let the big Females go ...they are the future of walleye fishing in the Grand! We all work hard to make fishing like it is for us all....  Thanks for a Great Weekend ...Fishmaster
Right on...nice catch !!!!!  great report & pics too..  .sounds like thats the place to be....cheers
Those are some nice looking eyes wtg  rob
